  "body": "When I work on #726, I used a `beacon` node to connect to `dev` node and start/stop them, then the test cannot exit so I have to use `--exit` flag in package.json\r\n\r\nSince we should not connect `beacon` node to `dev` node thru shared state, I don't have this issue anymore but it's worth to investigate.\r\n\r\nTo reproduce, write an e2e test:\r\n+ Start a dev node with 8 validators\r\n+ Start another dev node without validator\r\n+ Wait for blocks to be received on the 2nd node thru initial/regular sync\r\n+ Make sure we can start/stop/sync all nodes smoothly in the test",
